{
  "stem": "2906.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They ?] [? are ?] [? cold ?] or something for the wind.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they didn't give us one time to eat for two days, nothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I felt like, oh, I walk-- walked out, and I faint.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because-- and then when I open my eyes, two girls were pouring water on me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were two boys, they didn't eat for themselves, saw me the way I'm always dying.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were running maybe 50 miles to the headquarters and said, if you give-- don't give us food, we'll all die there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they sent us something to eat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "From there, I used to go with another girl, [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Viet ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Litsop, ?] and we find we-- that the Uzbeks used to live in tents.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they-- they had more food to eat than we.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we went to exchange this stuff for-- for corn.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We walked in the woods maybe 50 miles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Two girls going in the woods.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They could kill us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They could rape us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They could do anything with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We didn't see anybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we come close to this-- where all Uzbeks live, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And a big dog was running.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "A dog from the woods that can kill people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it-- the dog was running straight to us, and I thought that's-- we finished.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't know from where, from a [? sham, ?] a man came, a Uzbek.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He called his dog.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "This was something a miracle because we didn't expect to leave.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We went there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We exchanged these for a little bit, and we came back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You think we went again there because [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Inga ?] was so terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We had to go-- again there.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
